channel.title: Colors - Trojanian [WIP, Collab?]
channel.description:
Hey, y'all. It's me. Anyone wanna see what they can do with an old project of mine that didn't work out too well? I made it to fit a melody I was to write but couldn't. I kinda wrote a chorus, though. Kinda... It's under the sound called Fragment and starts at Scene 5, but I forgot to turn it on. You can mess around with that, too. Also tried to add a drop but was an **epic fail**. Enough talking for me, though. Let's see what happens with this.
